ical-thinking" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-text">Critical Thinking</span></a></li></ol></details></li></ol></details></li><li data-type="page" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic"><a href="a-fundamentals-of-physics-and-chemistry-important-to-microbiology" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-number">A</span><span class="os-divider"> | </span><span data-type="" itemprop="" class="os-text">Fundamentals of Physics and Chemistry Important to Microbiology</span></a></li><li data-type="page" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic"><a href="b-mathematical-basics" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-number">B</span><span class="os-divider"> | </span><span data-type="" itemprop="" class="os-text">Mathematical Basics</span></a></li><li data-type="page" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic"><a href="c-metabolic-pathways" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-number">C</span><span class="os-divider"> | </span><span data-type="" itemprop="" class="os-text">Metabolic Pathways</span></a></li><li data-type="page" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic"><a href="d-taxonomy-of-clinically-relevant-microorganisms" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-number">D</span><span class="os-divider"> | </span><span data-type="" itemprop="" class="os-text">Taxonomy of Clinically Relevant Microorganisms</span></a></li><li data-type="page" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic" aria-label="Current Page"><a href="e-glossary" class="styled__ContentLink-sc-18yti3s-1 cRIWDW"><span class="os-number">E</span><span class="os-divider"> | </span><span data-type="" itemprop="" class="os-text">Glossary</span></a></li><li data-type="eob-dropdown" class="styled__NavItem-sc-18yti3s-2 lcPtic"><details class="Details-xi326o-3 iboMxh styled__NavDetails-sc-18yti3s-6 fFBOM"><summary class="Details__Summary-xi326o-2 styled__Summary-sc-18yti3s-3 hLZWY